Text: It's about to get turbulent in here! Take care you don't get sucked in!
She's hidden herself! Find her quickly, or you'll be in for a world of pain!
All right, let's see how well you handle the big girl.
I'm the only one fit to protect her...
The Light will cleanse your sins!
Come! Show me your strength!
Let's try something else.
It's time we settled this.
Only I can protect her!
To think that this could be born from my memories...
That creature is passing on its aether!
The Light's so strong, I can't sense anything else...
I sense a surge in aether...
The blade is imbued with Light!
Wait... Didn't Gaia do something like this?
We can't fail here! We can't!
Defeat the Fatebreaker
I've toyed with you long enough.
No... She still needs me...
Defeat the Cloud of Darkness
No light could ever reach us...
We shall engulf everything in our shadow...
By the power of Darkness, we call forth life, boundless and irrepressible.
The Darkness swallows all, even the ground beneath your feet.
Clinging to one another will only hasten your descent...
With balance comes life, insatiable and all-consuming.
We shall return all to nothingness.
Hope, despair...they are what feeds us...
Unleash the shadows!
I will imitate your every move. When you attack, I attack. When you cast a spell, I'll cast a spell.
...So you seek to do perfectly nothing, perfectly? A clever tactic, but I have the entire Masked Carnivale to mimic.
What's taking so long!? Drop the performance art and go for the throat, just like you've seen me doing business!
Very well. I shall emulate your way of “doing business.”

Behold the essence of mimicry...
I answer your arcane assault in kind!

Anything you can do, I can do better...
A strike for a strike!
Protect Alisaie!
Channel aether to Alisaie!
Defeat the 2nd Order rocksplitter!
Channel more aether to Alisaie!
The girl seeks to harm the patriarch with vile magicks! Kill her! Slaughter, slay, kill!
Not if we have anything to say about it!
<split(<String>ObjectParameter(1)</String>, ,1)>─draw the golems to me! I'll deal with them all at once!
...Yes, it's ready! Go, Angelo!
Ugh, his tempering is too severe... \\<huff> I can't finish the job...
So one person's aether alone is not enough...
They're targeting Alisaie! Everyone, gather close!
Alphinaud! Let us lend Alisaie our aether!
Thanks, you two... I'll give it another try!
Ungh... I am nearing my limit...
Seven hells, there's too many...
Leave this to me! Stand clear, all of you!
Of all the reckless things... Alisaie─now's your chance!
All right! Please... Please let this work!
\\<huff> Almost there... \\<puff> <split(<String>ObjectParameter(1)</String>, ,1)>, please lend me your aether too!
Hehehe, you're dead now, girl! Finished, done for, dead!
No, Admiral! It's too dangerous!
I made my decision before I came here. No matter what it costs me, Limsa will have peace.
Slay the last one! Exterminate, destroy, slay!
Thank you! It will work this time, I promise!
Ugh, just what we need...
Bombs! We can't let them get near Alisaie!
Curses, more of them... Spread out and hold them off!
<split(<String>ObjectParameter(1)</String>, ,1)>, a little more aether! Just a little more, and I can finish this!
Defeat the Shadowkeeper

By your sacrifice, a warrior born...
I will show you no mercy, and expect none in return!

I am the Shadowkeeper!
There is no escape from me!
Cloaked in shadow, I lie in wait!
Death stalks at every turn!
Your shadow is mine to command!
Stabbed in the back, in more ways than one!
My world, consumed by Darkness. The source of my power...
All shadow is my dominion, and yours is no exception!
For all your strength, you are helpless to resist!

This is the end of our adventure.
You meant the world to me...
Defeat Misija and her imperial troops!
Defeat Delta Gabriel!
Take no prisoners. I want them all dead!
あの金色の機体は、私が引き付けましょう！

解放者殿は、ミーシィヤと、
その他の魔導兵器を頼みます……！
Admirable... But futile nonetheless. Ready the delta armor!
皆さん、私のところへ集まってください！
くっ……皆さん、ご無事ですか……！？

あの攻撃を耐え抜いただと……！？
だが、これで終いと思うなよ！

New magitek armor!? When did they find the time to─
No matter. We've come too far to retreat now.
We must divide and conquer, Blade <split(<String>ObjectParameter(1)</String>, ,2)>. I will draw this one's attention!
I will see to Misija. The remaining magitek armor is yours.
Round
Clear staging node A
Clear staging node B
Clear staging node C
Clear staging node D
Clear the ascension platform
Clear Beyond
This is the tower's network. Its digital consciousnesses are here.
Don't waste time trying to understand. We're here to kill the enemy. That's all.
What, aren't you enjoying yourselves?
You know what will happen to the sphere's creations when it's destroyed.
Don't worry about it. There's no actual meaning behind anything machines do.
It's locked.
Right─I'll hack the door, you infiltrate the network and take down any guards.
We're in! Let's go.

Here we go again.
Hacking in three...two...!
Whatever they're planning, we need to stop them before it's too late!

To live...is to know loneliness...
To live...is to know love...

I'll live as many times as it takes...
I'll die as many times as it takes...
To know... To know... To know...
They're all─ No! I don't want to be alone...
Let your voices...be heard...
Sing with me...
Such...delights... Did you...have fun?
You will be among the first to see the new world...
Destroy the target.
...But we still have some time. Why not enjoy it?

Multiple heat signatures coming from around the target.
Be ready!
Can you hear it? The final song...
We've waited so long to throw these gates wide...
Let the light in!
Where...?
All memory lives within me.
It's manipulating the space around us.
So many dreams slumber here...
Right below us!
Each memory's form is unique.
Watch the periphery!

We will sooなく...danger...the traんろ.
To ensure your safety...pleassssさイ...
Again!?
The final song...just for you.
You'll need to match wavelengths to create interference.
You would render all this meaningless?
You will soon find out how lowly you are.
They're going to fall. Move!

AH♪
               ah♪
ah♪ ah♪
Even if you defeat us... Do you really think you'll win?
We're prepared to fight until the end. Yours, or ours.

You fight and fight and fight...
You're made that way, after all.
You have so little control over your nature...
All you can do is watch as the world falls to ruin.
A logic virus! It's interfering with my hacking!
Destroy its core!
We made it.
Not half bad.
Your little alliance is pointless.
You'll never compare to us.

Ahahaha! You probably think you're clever.
But we've had just about enough...
Massive energy readings! Don't take your eyes off it.
Self-replication! There's another on the side!
Get as far away as you can!
It'll knock us off if we're not careful.
Ahahaha! You'll never eliminate us...
A defense program. Choose your target carefully.
You need to destroy the obstructing consciousnesses from inside the network.
Something's coming... Don't forget about that copy.
An energy signal! Watch which way it turns.
Defeat the Telophoroi troops
Locate the lunar primal
Defeat the enemy forces
Defeat Lunar Odin and defend the aetherial confluence
Defeat Lunar Ravana and defend the aetherial confluence
Defeat Lunar Ifrit and defend the aetherial confluence

Listen well, friends.
The Telophoroi are sweeping across Carteneau.

As for the Ascian, he was briefly sighted above the battlefield, but has since vanished.
He likely intends to watch events unfold from afar.

Thus far, the movements of the lunar primals have proven difficult to predict.
Even when poised to ambush our troops, they instead withdraw for some unknown reason...
Whatever the Telophoroi's plan may be, the primals are our primary targets.
Understood! They will not elude the Scions for long!
Let us divide our forces that we may locate the primals more swiftly. Thancred, Y'shtola, and I shall head east...
Then I'll go west. <split(<String>ObjectParameter(1)</String>, ,1)>, Alphinaud─ Come with me.
I'll concentrate my efforts on the tempered. With luck, I should have the chance to cure some of them.
I will keep them occupied! The rest of you, seek out the primals!
Th-There are so many of them...
I won't be curing anyone at this rate... We'll have to incapacitate them first!
Their tempering has gone too far to treat them here on the battlefield...
With this degree of physical alteration, I fear they are beyond help. Imperials or no, I hate to see them in such pain...
We must see that their suffering is not prolonged!
No more reinforcements, at least for the time being... Is everyone all right?
Is that...Odin? So the time has come to pit my blade against his. Follow my lead!
Leave the chains to me! Urianger, it's your turn to act as shield!
This does not bode well... We'd best brace ourselves!
Ugh... Such strength! It will take all three of us to protect the confluence!
But first, Thancred doth require our aid!
Odin is preparing to strike again! Stay out of his reach, but guarding the confluence must come first!
He yet stands... A glutton for punishment, it would seem.
In which case, I'd be glad to oblige him!
So it falls to us to protect the confluence from this fiend...
That must be Ravana! A formidable opponent, by all accounts, but so are we!
Like moths to the flame... We have to keep them from the confluence, but there are so many!
Then allow me! A quick casting of Break should buy us time!

That was a little close for comfort...
But now's our chance!
He's gathering aether... G'raha, try stopping him with Break!
I have a way of breaking his defenses, but I'll need time. Keep him occupied!
Understood! Let us hope that Break works as intended...
All right, I'm ready... It's now or never!
Lunar Ifrit... The one Arenvald and Fordola encountered!
This one is not to be taken lightly. Be on your guard.
Whatever those are, they bode ill for us. Smash them to pieces, before it's too late!
More of them!? Our foe seeks to destroy the confluence, and us along with it!
So, it's come to this...
